		<td><b>Re: Speaking of polarity... (APU related)</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The idea of +1 and -1 (positive and negative samples on square waves, duty cycles) came from the defunct Nofrendo.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
